data.description: Lovely home in Lakeview Heights with a true master suite!!  This spacious 1900 square foot home features three bedrooms, two bathrooms, updated kitchen, fresh paint, and hardwood floors.  Master suite bathroom includes double sinks and a large tile, double-headed shower. Additional perks: single car carport in the front, carpet in the master bedroom and den, and garage, carport, and workshop in the backyard (perfect for the diy-er in your life). Pride of ownership is very evident throughout.  Roof was replaced in June of 2023. This home is move in ready and is conveniently located to the interstate to get you where you need to be!!
